# Locally-built tarballs (CI builds these fresh from react-native-runtimes)
**/vendor/*.tgz

# JS
**/node_modules/

# react-native-runtimes / Metro generated
**/.threaded-runtime/
**/.expo/
**/.metro-health-check*

# iOS (Pods + build artifacts; .xcworkspace is regenerated by pod install)
**/ios/Pods/
**/ios/build/
**/*.xcworkspace
**/DerivedData/

# Android build artifacts (keep the source for bare apps)
**/android/.gradle/
**/android/build/
**/android/app/build/
**/android/.cxx/
**/android/local.properties

# misc
.DS_Store
*.log
package-lock.json
